                "description": "A list of cost allocation tags to be added to this resource. Tags are comma-separated key,value pairs (e.g. Key=<code>myKey</code>, Value=<code>myKeyValue</code>. You can include multiple tags as shown following: Key=<code>myKey</code>, Value=<code>myKeyValue</code> Key=<code>mySecondKey</code>, Value=<code>mySecondKeyValue</code>."
              }
            ]
